{"tid":873553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（記者真好做3）有連登仔出咗個post，話發現五十歲嘅外母曾經拍過一套叫《卿xxx》嘅三級片","createTime":"2018-10-23T13:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T16:13:01.000Z","uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c53a9a731d5295b865c5550d3593c7b24db526da","tid":873553,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤 喱騷 Chapman To&rsquo;s late show - <br />\n<br />\n有連登仔出咗個post，話發現五十歲嘅外母曾經拍過一套叫《卿xxx》嘅三級片，片中有露三點扑野嘅大膽演出。佢仲話外母後生時身材拍得住周秀娜。有一次老婆出咗差，屋企得返佢同外母兩個，外母就向佢坦白，話當年因為年少無知，以為可以同方x信有大膽親熱戲，先俾人氹到拍咸片。 連登仔隨即安慰唏噓嘅外母，仲搞到自己硬晒鈦。喺呢個咁悲傷嘅倫常家庭慘況，一班仆乖嘅網民，竟然仲要追問故事嘅下落！你哋班粉皮想知嘅話自己去search「Mother-in-law」系列啦！仲問！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/215406_915cde473acfcf7b237967e467ca2b62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F215406_915cde473acfcf7b237967e467ca2b62.png&h=29a1ac84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7279c7e92b13630f8fe05c9b4a7be0cc9ce10acf","tid":873553,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.657815361024154/1244300209042330/?type=3&amp;source=48u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fofficialchapmanto%2Fphotos%2Fa.657815361024154%2F1244300209042330%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D48u&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=137f03cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.657815361024154/1244300209042330/?type=3&amp;source=48u</a>"},{"pid":"34c3899a1cf6bad451c6bf87f55f52247f8ab1f1","tid":873553,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"點面對拍過三級片嘅外母？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/870128\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/870128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red